    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Describes the fashionable world of dressmakers and dressmaking establishments collectively, including all that contributes to it culturally. For the practice and industry of dressmaking associated with these houses, use "couture."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
